{"title":"Backcountry Announces Mountain Bike Apparel Line","link":"https://theradavist.com/backcountry-mountain-bike-apparel-line/","date":1711643343000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/ROCLFLPR.jpg?fit=1200,1200&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/ROCLFLPR.jpg?w=1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/ROCLFLPR.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/ROCLFLPR.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/ROCLFLPR.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Online retailer <a href=\"https://backcountry.tnu8.net/rQK6Pj\" target=\"_blank\">Backcountry</a> just announced a complete <a href=\"https://backcountry.tnu8.net/rQK6Pj\" target=\"_blank\">mountain bike apparel line</a> for men and women. Find some of our favorites below.<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/BackCountry_MTB_clothing.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/BackCountry_MTB_clothing.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/BackCountry_MTB_clothing.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/BackCountry_MTB_clothing.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/BackCountry_MTB_clothing.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/BIS.jpg?fit=1200,1200&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/BIS.jpg?w=1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/BIS.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/BIS.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/BIS.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>For the forthcoming warmer days, there is the Slickrock Bike Shortis offered in 9 and 11 inch inseams for men and women ($99). The button-up MTB jerseys ($89.00) for men and women come in a variety of patterns and colors. There are button up trail shirts, long sleeve jerseys ($79.00), women’s short liners ($79.00), and more.</p>\n<p>Check out the full drop at <a href=\"https://backcountry.tnu8.net/rQK6Pj\" target=\"_blank\">Backcountry</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/backcountry-mountain-bike-apparel-line/\">Backcountry Announces Mountain Bike Apparel Line</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"2c6e9adacc83b90ff439cff8ff542e5c6e56fd98fbab53c86638bea4cc83372e","category":"Cycling"}